C" data-media-id=3D"611711" class=3D"lightbox-image">
     =20
    <a href=3D"https://www.nist.gov/sites/default/files/styles/2800_x_2800_=
limit/public/images/2021/05/21/dry_hopping_an_IPA.JPG?itok=3DKeZqXJ8C" aria=
